似要微信book</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無話邊一位醫師會好d？<br />\n我見有好多個揀但都約滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1330195d4de7260c17e8413a826355bf9308bf","tid":52152,"uid":11940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T09:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我未試過翻大陸睇醫生 係直接去就睇得？<br />\n定係上網book時間？<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jt91.com/herbalist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jt91.com%2Fherbalist%2F&d=dn0RRCmRY%2FO3t512OqD4d3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=2003e5b9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jt91.com/herbalist/</a><br />\n係咪呢個<br />\n唔該曬你！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深圳市中醫院推拿科 ，幾好，好似要微信book</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無話邊一位醫師會好d？<br />\n我見有好多個揀但都約滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry想問多樣<br />\n做gym會唔會有影響？<br />\n會唔會越做越衰？"},{"pid":"306f3802bbcde385533396d1ee2f98b3888e544d","tid":52152,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深圳市中醫院推拿科 ，幾好，好似要微信book</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無話邊一位醫師會好d？<br />\n我見有好多個揀但都約滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nsorry想問多樣<br />\n做gym會唔會有影響？<br />\n會唔會越做越衰？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實門診部得幾位醫生，個個都差唔多，如果你有傷的話我建議你好返7-8成先好做，做運動的確可加強肌肉，韌帶能力，可以叫做預防而唔係治療，治療方面始終要靠醫生，始終而家未清楚你係咩問題，好難答到你太多"},{"pid":"2c0fd212000b92196795af7832f4ebc451ee86a4","tid":52152,"uid":20972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:50:06.000Z","msg":"認真：<br />\n搵印度master 做瑜珈，我頸、肩丶手丶背、腳丶坐骨嘅痛、痺等等因為咁做返好。有時D骨走咗位，就去&quot;明療&quot;度整返好。本身先天條件並不好，但做三個月已經可以拱橋、半年已經可以一字馬，D筋鬆咗，D肌肉鬆咗，練返D核心肌力，先至係治標同治本。搵D master 本身喺印度除咗瑜珈，仲有治療嘅學歷同經驗最好，佢地會了解咗你嘅情況，睇住你，俾啱你程度嘅嘢你做。唔洗上私人堂，上大班就夠。如果你覺得女人先會做瑜珈，咁就試彼拉提斯，不過彼拉提斯貴過瑜珈。<br />\n另外，嗰個枕頭，每日低頭嘅時間太長，個枕頭就幫你條頸每晚有幾個鐘保持相反嘅姿勢，即係自然嘅姿勢，我最初半個月用佢條頸係覺得冤嘅，佢慢慢幫我條頸移返啱位，冇咁快老化。<br />\n仲有呢個坐壂，我喺日本買到嘅。坐壂、背壂我買過不下四丶五個，呢個真正最好，一定要中間有粒嘢突出嚟呢款，舊款係冇嘅，用咗佢之後坐得耐條腰唔會痛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VFEH3zA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVFEH3zA.jpg&h=502af0cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"965b035bf0d1c06088499675345621d8c454a0ef","tid":52152,"uid":66154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"我都係 痛到係咁扭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲會耳嗚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4558170786f1629f60699d3ecedfbe1d2397f709","tid":52152,"uid":69778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"注意自己姿勢<br />\n唔好成日坐/dup低頭<br />\n多啲拉筋 得閒去做下運動<br />\n<br />\n以前都有類似病痛 宜家好番好多<br />\n祝巴打快啲好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bdc72902936f5f14bc41ad00fc91d8bfbee915","tid":52152,"uid":69778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote][quote]<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6ebaszj8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6ebaszj8&h=fc071e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講明，過程好痛，但睇完兩次之後包你有好轉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住睇天后脊醫王俊華<br />\n超聲波按摩，啪幾下骨，上機扭幾下<br />\n全程20分鐘就收我500，重要日日睇<br />\n睇左成個月都重係痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nexactly<br />\n我都有睇過佢 絕大部分時間都係超聲波按摩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗成個月都冇改善 後尾轉咗睇物理治療 個物理治療師聽到我經歷之後第一句就問 做乜要睇脊醫 做乜要啪骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b038f999f5df1fa95aece4665386b733a35ee44f","tid":52152,"uid":55018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D0G7eO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D0G7eO.jpg&h=78019909&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45881cd3c2f34f4a22c5e4eba649781935d3d758","tid":52152,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D0G7eO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D0G7eO.jpg&h=78019909&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係佢本人、朋友定客人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23413a040760597d70cd5fa792e3473699ce59ee","tid":52152,"uid":28786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T14:30:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3D0G7eO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3D0G7eO.jpg&h=78019909&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係本人、佢朋友定客人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}